snippet.title: UnReal World official trailer 2016
snippet.description:
UnReal World is a unique roguelike RPG set in the Far North during the late Iron-Age and emphasized on survival in the harsh wilderness. Trailer features gameplay of upcoming version 3.30 to be published in late February 2016.

UnReal World homepage:
http://www.unrealworld.fi

UnReal World on Steam:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/351700
